  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a relaxing puzzle game and unlock rooms in the house to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find objects for the puzzles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat the Simon Game</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crack the pair matching game</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look for clues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the riddles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve more than 20 puzzles based on logic</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your time, unlock rooms and have fun in a calm, cozy little house. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a relaxing puzzle game and unlock rooms in the house to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find objects for the puzzles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat the Simon Game</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crack the pair matching game</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look for clues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the riddles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve more than 20 puzzles based on logic</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your time, unlock rooms and have fun in a calm, cozy little house. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
